Extract the source files into the proper directories such that:

If choosing lib3ds-2.0.0 RC1 (lib3ds-20080909.zip)
then the directory structure is:
3rdparty -> lib3ds-2.0.0 -> lib3ds -> lib3ds.h

If choosing lib3ds-1.3.0 (lib3ds-1.3.0.zip)
then the directory structure is:
3rdparty -> lib3ds-1.3.0 -> src -> mesh.h

If build QGLViewer then:
3rdparty -> libQGLViewer-2.3.9 -> QGLViewer -> qglviewer.h